{"tid":2301172,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"關寶慧拍三級片遭PS變全裸　一度患上抑鬱症","createTime":"2020-11-26T05:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T08:06:41.000Z","uid":318316,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfc7d4fada86c35e4c927434c8de298028d9489","tid":2301172,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T05:41:02.000Z","msg":"演藝出身的關寶慧，90年代開始在港產片圈發展，多年來以飾演性格潑的配角為主，到90年代尾更接連演了幾部三級片，當中在《男人胸女人Home》擔任女主角，博盡全裸演出，可惜未能為她的演藝事業有太大起色。相隔多年，關寶慧透露當年有著住泳衣，劇組靠PS將她變成全裸，她無辜成了脫星，形象太受影響，後來更患上抑鬱症。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201122/407272146948067328947581.jpeg/43JtYihMzZmvW-B1xicWjJqSh2jVr88f0OcCcNDnAnA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201122%2F407272146948067328947581.jpeg%2F43JtYihMzZmvW-B1xicWjJqSh2jVr88f0OcCcNDnAnA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=26f7b56b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201122/407272873691320320516480.jpeg/FV7Ibb_c37gI_DBJtTwrflozuDDwSwvSTo4Eo06OBKM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201122%2F407272873691320320516480.jpeg%2FFV7Ibb_c37gI_DBJtTwrflozuDDwSwvSTo4Eo06OBKM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=539338c0&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201122/407272884215484416731240.jpeg/0r4CuFFbTrLy9ls9UvLX6n3OexByMIm3HrIOVB6yDlQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201122%2F407272884215484416731240.jpeg%2F0r4CuFFbTrLy9ls9UvLX6n3OexByMIm3HrIOVB6yDlQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=555dbd52&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/552309/%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%B8%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BAhome-%E9%97%9C%E5%AF%B6%E6%85%A7%E6%8B%8D%E4%B8%89%E7%B4%9A%E7%89%87%E9%81%ADps%E8%AE%8A%E5%85%A8%E8%A3%B8-%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E6%82%A3%E4%B8%8A%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1%E7%97%87#media_id=5746465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F552309%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2583%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BAhome-%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E6%2585%25A7%25E6%258B%258D%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%2581%25ADps%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25A3%25B8-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2582%25A3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%258A%2591%25E9%25AC%25B1%25E7%2597%2587%23media_id%3D5746465&h=956c8b47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201122/407272869349953536193042.jpeg/txQLZQQWiFRpicFKovZ_V-hj6lRPgv3vjpADd46QA3c?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201122%2F407272869349953536193042.jpeg%2FtxQLZQQWiFRpicFKovZ_V-hj6lRPgv3vjpADd46QA3c%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3402e1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n90年代尾，港產三級片已是「尾水」，關寶慧卻突然演起了情色電影，當中在朱偉光執導的《男人胸女人Home》中擔當起女主角，全裸上陣與鄭浩南演大膽情慾場面，雖然票房不到200萬，電影口碑亦不佳，但關寶慧一脫就引起不少回響。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是去年關寶慧受訪時透露，當年是受騙而成為脫星，事源拍攝宣傳海報時，關寶慧全程穿上泳衣，可是成品卻變成她一絲不掛僅以手掩胸，加上是三級片的關係，觀眾以為她想一脫成名，慘遭標籤成三級片女星足足20年，有指關寶慧為此患上抑鬱症。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/552309/%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%B8%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BAhome-%E9%97%9C%E5%AF%B6%E6%85%A7%E6%8B%8D%E4%B8%89%E7%B4%9A%E7%89%87%E9%81%ADps%E8%AE%8A%E5%85%A8%E8%A3%B8-%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E6%82%A3%E4%B8%8A%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1%E7%97%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F552309%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2583%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BAhome-%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E6%2585%25A7%25E6%258B%258D%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%2581%25ADps%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25A3%25B8-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2582%25A3%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%258A%2591%25E9%25AC%25B1%25E7%2597%2587&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=6c0e0cf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://